==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Ryder
<hw>Ry"der</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>A clause
added to a document; a rider. See <er>Rider</er>.</def>
<mark>[Obs.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <ety>[D. <ets>rijder</ets>, properly, a rider.]</ety>
<def>A gold coin of Zealand [Netherlands] equal to 14 florins, about
$5.60 (ca. 1910).</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Rye</ent>⟦br⟧
